title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
subtitle: GTA+
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (February 6 - March 3) will also receive:

— The Vapid FMJ (Super)
— 2X Rewards on Bunker Sell Missions
— 50% off Bunker Properties and their Upgrades and Modifications
— The Honkers Tie-Dye Hoodie and Honkers Tie-Dye Hat
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
